Key Match Events: South Africa won by 4 wickets (with 7 balls remaining)
Sybrand Engelbrecht top-scored for Netherlands with a 45-ball 40
Post-Match Reflections: David Miller tamed the demons of Adelaide 2022
Miscellaneous Highlights: The win was set up by the South Africa fast bowlers
The pitch didn't play anywhere as badly as the scorecard suggested
Others: Quinton de Kock was run out without facing a ball
Reeza Hendricks got a peach from Logan van Beek that angled in and straightened to hit the top of off
Vivian Kingma struck twice in the powerplay
